{
  "texts": [
    "This component is specifically designed for new e-commerce platforms that lack substantial historical user-item interaction data.",
    "The primary aim is to generate effective and relevant product recommendations using available product descriptions.",
    "The methodology here is inspired by the work of Lops, de Gemmis, and Semeraro (2011), who emphasized the significance of content-based recommendation systems.",
    "The Home Depot product descriptions dataset is used for initial data analysis (Home Depot Product Search Relevance Dataset, n.d.), undergoing preprocessing to standardize the format and remove irrelevant information.",
    "The TF-IDF vectorization and K-Means clustering of product descriptions follow the approaches discussed by Lops, de Gemmis, and Semeraro (2011), allowing us to group products into distinct clusters based on the similarity of their descriptions."
  ]
}